Result.label: Forecast Summary
Result.Data:
"Forecasting uses statistical trends in your data to predict future values. It automatically tests multiple forecasting models against the specified data items and then selects the best model for each one.
Forecast: Total_Requests - By Apr 2025 (6 time periods), Total_Requests is forecast to be 1.7K with a 95% confidence interval between 943 and 2.5K. The forecast represents an approximate decrease of 82 (4.49%) from the Oct 2024 value of 1.8K. - The selected model is Seasonal Exponential Smoothing."

Result.label: "What If"
Result.StringTable: "Goal seeking determines the value of each underlying factor that is required to achieve a specified target response value. Change the future values of one or more forecasts to generate a new goal seeking scenario. This information window includes descriptive statistics when you apply a new goal seeking scenario." "Scenario analysis creates a forecast that is based on hypothetical future values for one or more underlying factors. Change the future values of one or more underlying factors to generate a new scenario. This information window includes descriptive statistics when you apply a new scenario."
